\f1\b MSI Center
\f0\b0  is notorious for bundling the Ryzen Master SDK and various AMD drivers during its initial setup or "Live Update" scans.\
While the SDK is optional, the 
\f1\b AMD Chipset Software
\f0\b0  is a different story. It is a critical collection of drivers that allows Windows to communicate efficiently with your motherboard\'92s hardware.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
